ass="cdata"><span> Array (     [country_code] =&gt; CZ     [latitude] =&gt; 50.08333     [longitude] =&gt; 14.43333     [comments] =&gt;  ) Array (     [country_code] =&gt; CZ     [latitude] =&gt; 50.08333     [longitude] =&gt; 14.43333     [comments] =&gt;  ) </span></div>     </div>    </div>   </span>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/class.datetimezone.php">DateTimeZone</a></div></div>
